OL,3,CMan found guilty of killing football
OL,4,Cfan outside Blackpool pub
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of killing
OL,7,Fa Blackpool FC fan in a post-match
OL,8,Fbrawl at a pub.
OL,10,FTony Johnson, 55, suffered a fatal
OL,11,Fhead injury after being punched by
OL,12,FJake Balmforth during a disturbance
OL,13,Foutside the Manchester pub on the
OL,14,FPromenade.
OL,16,FThe incident occurred after the
OL,17,FBlackpool and Burnley game at
OL,18,FBloomfield Road earlier in the day on
OL,19,F4 March 2023.
