OL,3,CMan found guilty of killing football
OL,4,Cfan outside Blackpool pub
OL,6,FBalmforth, 35, of Tarvin Close,
OL,7,FBurnley, was found guilty of
OL,8,Fmanslaughter on Tuesday 6 May by a
OL,9,Fjury at Preston Crown Court following
OL,10,Fa six-day trial.
OL,12,FThe trial heard how Mr Johnson had
OL,13,Fbeen among a group of Blackpool fans
OL,14,Fwho gathered outside the Manchester
OL,15,Fpub which, on the day, was a
OL,16,Fdesignated 'away' pub for Burnley
OL,17,Fsupporters.
