OL,4,Cfan outside Blackpool pub
OL,6,FA disturbance followed between
OL,7,FBlackpool and Burnley fans, and CCTV
OL,8,Ffootage showed Balmforth punch Mr
OL,9,FJohnson once in the face.
OL,11,FHe was taken to the Blackpool Victoria
OL,12,FHospital but very sadly was pronounced
OL,13,Fdead on 6th March having not regained
OL,14,Fconsciousness.
OL,16,FDet Chief Insp Andy Fallows of
OL,17,FLancashire Police's Force Major
OL,18,FInvestigation Team, said: "My thoughts
OL,19,Fremain first and foremost with Tony
OL,20,FJohnson's family and loved ones.
