OL,6,F"During the trial over the last few
OL,7,Fdays, they have had the distressing
OL,8,Fexperience of having to relive the
OL,9,Fevents of that evening in March 2023.
OL,11,F"This case highlights what the tragic
OL,12,Fconsequences can be when violence
OL,13,Fbreaks out."
OL,15,FBalmforth was remanded into custody
OL,16,Funtil his sentencing on 22 May.
OL,18,FNine other men who pleaded guilty to
OL,19,Faffray in relation to the disturbance,
OL,20,Fwill be sentenced at a later date.
